snippet.title: Hyper Scape: Season 1 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Hyper Scape’s Season 1 starts August 11 on PC, Xbox One and PlayStation4! In Season 1, you will discover a new gun, a new hack, new limited-time game modes and a 100 tier Battle Pass!


Follow HyperScape:
Website: https://www.hyperscape.com
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/hyperscapegame
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/hyperscapegame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hyperscapegame
